{"tid":847602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★馬鞍山KFC「仙氣」女經理網上爆紅","createTime":"2018-10-04T09:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T10:50:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"439d3a3fd3c8fbb3505035e69116fa0a19a09e64","tid":847602,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1935116/org/d12727966988ad3a7cddd17fd476f311.jpg/WPquj3PlMoQjfLPZFPnKQt6k8xCnnIyrX0w2f19MNn8?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1935116%2Forg%2Fd12727966988ad3a7cddd17fd476f311.jpg%2FWPquj3PlMoQjfLPZFPnKQt6k8xCnnIyrX0w2f19MNn8%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=3e1b8ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山居民常言該區為「美食沙漠」，較早前有集團在該區開設連鎖餐廳，已令馬鞍山居民歡喜若狂。近日有網民指，區內一商場裏的KFC新店長期大排長龍，相信除了食物價錢大眾化外，更因該店女經理「仙氣」滿滿，吸引不少食客行注目禮。有關社交媒體帖文更在網上廣傳，令「仙氣」女經理人氣急升。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者昨日（3日）到店內直擊，發現該曾姓女經理正忙個不停，為客人奉上一份又一份美食，直至放工前最後一刻仍做到無停手。她接受《香港01》訪問時說：「呢排係多咗騷擾，過一排會無嘢㗎啦！」又指自己未想過要出名，就算在網上爆紅亦會如常工作，過正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1934739/org/7c2b6966f77fa2995ddb02f2a3b54204.JPG/SV7H0KDzWMpsQ6GACTKEORA8StDUP8fIspLEaJeSxGg?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1934739%2Forg%2F7c2b6966f77fa2995ddb02f2a3b54204.JPG%2FSV7H0KDzWMpsQ6GACTKEORA8StDUP8fIspLEaJeSxGg%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=2106d674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山KFC大排長龍　食客覓「仙氣」女經理芳蹤<br />\n<br />\n有「美食沙漠」之稱的馬鞍山，早前開設首間吉野家時，不少人即蜂擁到該處光顧，更將其稱為「飯堂」，至於另一家台式連鎖壽司店爭鮮在區內開業，光顧的人龍更一度大打蛇餅。而最近在馬鞍山一個商場開業的KFC，更是人氣爆燈。<br />\n<br />\n日前有網民於社交網站上載相片，指馬鞍山一商場內的KFC長期大排長龍，原因是店內有一位「仙氣」女經理，該帖文在網上爆紅之外，更有不少網民專程到該店幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/243032/%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1kfc-%E4%BB%99%E6%B0%A3-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E6%9C%AA%E6%83%B3%E9%81%8E%E5%87%BA%E5%90%8D-%E6%9C%83%E5%A6%82%E5%B8%B8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F243032%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259E%258D%25E5%25B1%25B1kfc-%25E4%25BB%2599%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25B4%2585-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2590%258D-%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C&d=z2mhxptcnXvYxAH54PNQzUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7cb4641b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/243032/%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1kfc-%E4%BB%99%E6%B0%A3-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E6%9C%AA%E6%83%B3%E9%81%8E%E5%87%BA%E5%90%8D-%E6%9C%83%E5%A6%82%E5%B8%B8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C</a>"},{"pid":"3911e243470fd64857a8bcb2a0aedbaf7910fb35","tid":847602,"uid":62822,"like":28,"dislike":85,"score":-57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbdab81566ea7cb8f1ce6bf1c94733d4e24bb913","tid":847602,"uid":190328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3911e243470fd64857a8bcb2a0aedbaf7910fb35","tid":847602,"uid":62822,"like":28,"dislike":85,"score":-57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"比福記阿皮免費屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a63e25f728800f6190dd4bbe199a560fc87208","tid":847602,"uid":8949,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"點解老貓出post咁多負皮？"},{"pid":"c8ceb43df84ce4b8b32368b165b48170bc5687f0","tid":847602,"uid":2959,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"kfc係唔係靚女都要等半個鐘㗎啦排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709fc0f482a234982ec3ba5e252b9ffbc425fb02","tid":847602,"uid":5549,"like":7,"dislike":3,"